&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a dynamic, motivated individual to work with our friendly and hard working Ophthalmic team at Orsett.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will support the ward manager and lead the team to ensure the delivery of safe, individualised care to patients requiring ophthalmic surgeries.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ophthalmology is responsible for providing specialist ophthalmic care across MSE; we offer a 24 hour emergency service which you may become part of once you have become competent and confident in your practice.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Orsett Hospital is situated in a quiet village close to the M25 and lakeside shopping centre.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
